		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Caps do suck, even today. Most cheap PSU's buy cheap caps that dry QUICK because they're POS's, causing tons of failures. Any discount computer or PSU probably uses those caps, unlike my corsair 950 watt desktop PSU, which uses solid caps. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

